organic.title: The Queen's Medical Center – The Queen′s Health Systems
organic.snippet: The Queen's Medical Center, Honolulu's largest nonprofit hospital (575 beds), offers cancer, heart, neuroscience, emergency, and trauma care. It's a level one trauma center and was voted "Best Hospital in Honolulu" in 2017-2018.

organic.title: HHC - Queens Hospital Center (QHC) - NYC.gov
organic.snippet: Queens Hospital Center is a member of the Queens Health Network and affiliate of the Mount Sinai School of Medicine. Call (718) 883-3131 for appointments.

organic.title: Queens Patient & Visitors - NYC Health + Hospitals
organic.snippet: NYC Health + Hospitals/Queens offers primary care, pediatrics, geriatrics, and HIV care. They accept most insurance, offer discounts, and have multilingual services. Call 844-692-4692 for appointments.
